## Troubleshooting / SoluÃ§Ã£o de Problemas

- ORA-02236: Missing destination for OMF â€“ Set `db_create_file_dest`
- ORA-02199: Missing DATAFILE/TEMPFILE clause â€“ Specify file info or set OMF
- FRA errors: Always specify both path and size

